    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:12.000Z",
    "description": "Alright, I might be from LA, and I also might have an avocado toast recipe in this book—truly the ultimate stereotype. But let’s all just take a real step back and look at avocado toast. It is f—ing delicious. I don’t care who you are. If you enjoy avocado, it’s one of the greatest little snacks (or even a whole meal) that I can think to have. It’s perfectly rich and exciting to eat, yet you don’t feel sloppy after eating it. It’s a win-win.",
