    "description": "I think if my mom got to choose between putting up with my BS as a kid or having a lifetime supply of banana hot fudge sundaes, we’d be seeing a lot of empty sundae bowls right now. It’s one of her very favorites, and it’s an absolute class choice at ice cream shops. I’m bummed that it’s not ordered as much these days. This recipe will bring it back with just a touch of culinary intention.",
