    "updatedAt": "2024-09-18T10:32:20.000Z",
    "description": "I was originally just going to put a traditional carbonara here. Then I thought about it more and more—and there are chewier things outside of pasta. So the idea of making this recipe came to mind, and adapting tteokbokki into carbonara seemed like Italian sacrilege in the best way possible. It turns out, I didn’t regret it.",
    "yield": {
      "quantity": 2,
      "unit": "servings",
      "notes": "2 servings"
    },
