    "description": "Let me say this carefully: I hate kale. Well…I hate kale in most contexts. If you’re in the same boat, this one will be a true revelation. Either that, or you love kale and you didn’t realize it could be taken to such heights.",
    "yield": {
      "quantity": 2,
      "notes": "2–4"
    },
