    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:12.000Z",
    "description": "These nuggets represent beauty in simplicity. I kept the ingredients here pretty low-key. You can absolutely add any array of spices you’d like, or keep it the way it is. This chicken nugget is as good as the technique you put into it. If you are an expert chicken bread-er, then you will find this chicken nugget to satisfy all your chicken dreams.",
