    "description": "I honestly think it’s the name of this dish that turns people away. “Hey, Rick, you wanna go get Dutch babies down the street?” It just sounds weird. You should take a chance, though, because this is one of my favorite side dishes of all time for an unforgettable brunch…or really any time.",
