    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:11.000Z",
    "description": "Pulling pure liquid fat from your fatty animal meat is a really straightforward process; don’t overcomplicate it. This method will work with any solid animal fat you can think of. Use the extracted fats anytime you need cooking fat, like for frying or sautéing.",
