    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:12.000Z",
    "description": "This is the soup that calls your name as soon as the weather turns cold (or it does mine, at least). It’s a perfect food, in my opinion. Sweet caramelized onions, rich beef stock, crunchy bread, melty cheese—everything you could want in a single sip of soup.",
    "yield": {
      "quantity": 7,
      "notes": "7"
    },
