    "description": "This one of those foods you rarely see people making at home for some reason—it’s an “order at brunch” kind of thing. But the irony is that really all you need to do is dip a slice of bread in a milk-egg mixture and toast it. You have complete control over the flavor and texture, which is a big advantage to making your perfect French toast.",
