    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:12.000Z",
    "description": "In general, I think just the idea of a “fish taco” gets a bad rap. Maybe it’s because people are too busy thinking about something more familiar, like a carnitas or steak taco. I’m here to tell you that if there is anything to convert you to the world of fish tacos, this is it right here.",
