    "updatedAt": "2024-09-17T22:05:12.000Z",
    "description": "There was a point during the infancy of social media when people were putting a sunny-side up fried egg on literally everything. It’s delicious, but the idea of it has unfortunately been ruined by the internet (like many things). With that said, I do have a saving grace for you, and that is the humble soft-boiled egg. It’s great on its own, on top of some avocado toast, or floating in a bowl of ramen.",
    "yield": {
      "quantity": 4,
      "notes": "4"
    },
    "times": {
      "prepMinutes": 5,
      "cookMinutes": 7,
      "totalMinutes": 12
    },
