    "description": "I used to loathe the idea of making a cake. It was just never something I was that interested in, and the pastry chefs I worked with always made it seem unnecessarily difficult. This recipe exists to show you otherwise.",
    "yield": {
      "quantity": 1,
      "unit": "double-layer (9-inch/23-cm) cake (serves 12-15)",
      "notes": "1 double-layer (9-inch/23-cm) cake (serves 12–15)"
    },
    "times": {
      "prepMinutes": 25,
      "cookMinutes": 35,
      "totalMinutes": 60
    },
