    "description": "Almost my entire life I hated tomato soup. But this tomato soup was a revelation to me. It’s not weird and ketchup-tasting. It’s herbaceous, fragrant, lightly tart, fresh, and just a touch on the creamy side. Plus, grilled cheese makes everything better.",
